## docs/LICENSE_ATTRIBUTION_PLAN.md
headings: # License Attribution Plan | ## Hermes Reference | ## Policy | ## Attribution Record
early bullets: - Do not vendor the full Hermes repository. || - Do not blindly copy code. || - Prefer adapting architecture and reimplementing where practical. || - If code is copied, preserve original license notices. || - Track copied files and adaptation rationale under `third_party_licenses/`. || - Source repository and path || - Source commit or version if available || - License
